snippet.title: Socket (Genesis) - Longplay
snippet.description:
A longplay of Socket.

Socket, known in Japan as Time Dominator 1st, is a fast-paced platform game developed and published by Vic Tokai for the Mega Drive/Genesis. It was released on March 24, 1994 in North America and on March 25, 1994 in Japan. The game was not released in Europe or Australia.
